Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Jean Seberg and the FBI, 1979
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqrc0
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 21 Sep 1979
The detestable confession that confirms that the actress Jean Seberg's life was destroyed by J Edgar Hoover's 'dirty tricks' branch of the FBI.